#Text=Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 shot down over eastern Ukraine , killing 298
#Text=Saturday , July 19 , 2014
#Text=File photo from 2010 of Malaysia Airlines Boeing 777 9M-MRD , the aircraft that was shot down .
#Text=Image : Alan Wilson .
#Text=Malaysia Airlines
#Text=Flight 17
#Text=, a Boeing 777 , was shot down by a surface-to-air missile on Thursday according to US officials , over disputed eastern Ukraine by an unidentified party .

#Text=The flight , which departed Amsterdam Airport Schiphol in The Netherlands at 10:15 UTC en route to Kuala Lumpur International Airport in Malaysia , disappeared from radar at 13:15 UTC near Hrabove , a village in the Donetsk Oblast of Ukraine .
#Text=283 passengers and 15 crew were aboard the aircraft , all 298 in total perished .
#Text=The area the plane was flying over is a conflict zone currently between Ukrainian forces and pro- Russian separatist forces .
#Text=United States
#Text=officials confirmed the aircraft has been shot down , according to data from a surveillance satellite which showed the last trajectory and impact of the missile .
#Text=The missile is believed to be a Buk M1 surface-to-air missile which are believed to be in the hands of rebels according to reports from the area .
#Text=Flight path of Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 .
#Text=Image : Geordie Bosanko and cmglee .
#Text=So far no party has claimed responsibility for the attack .
#Text=Ukrainian officials denied the missile which shot down the airliner belonged to Ukraine .
#Text=Pavlo Klimkin
#Text=, Ukraine 's foreign minister , said to The Guardian , " We are absolutely sure and we checked yesterday that no missiles have been taken from the Ukrainian army " .

#Text=The Security Service of Ukraine ( SBU ) published on YouTube an alleged wiretap of separatist commanders and Russian intelligence officers discussing the shoot-down and acknowledging the aircraft shot down was civilian .

#Text=Meanwhile , Russia 's defense ministry has denied involvement , posting a statement on their website which read , " In view of various types of speculation concerning operations of the Russian armed forces in the areas bordering Ukraine , we affirm that the anti-aircraft means of the Russian armed forces did not operate in that region July 17 " .
#Text=Ukrainian president Petro Poroshenko said , " This was not an ' incident ' , this was not a ' catastrophe ' , this was a terrorist act " .
#Text=Malyasian prime minister Najib Razak , said , " If it transpires that the flight was shot down , we insist that the perpetrators must swiftly be brought to justice .
